SKU: 209916-854Product Description

Step into the Boca Wedge Flip and enjoy superb comfort combined with sleek, contemporary style. Featuring the plush LiteRide™ foam footbed, you’ll enjoy world-class comfort wherever you go. Plus, straps with stylish mini sequins make this an extremely wearable way to add shine. The Women’s Crocs Boca Sequin Wedge Flip offers premium comfort and style.

Boca Bling Flip Detail:

  • Versatile, modern styling for everyday wear
  • Easy flip-wedge silhouette with soft, molded toe posts
  • Straps with diamante embellishments on straps
  • Durable Croslite™ foam outsoles provide all-day support and comfort
  • LiteRide™ foam footbed: Revolutionary. Sink-in softness. Innovative comfort.
